      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Business Logic: Complex decision tree based on all conditions\nRules:\n- Deadline passed + escalated = ESCALATE_AND_NOTIFY\n- CRITICAL + not approved = IMMEDIATE_ESCALATION\n- HIGH + missing docs = REQUEST_DOCUMENTS_AND_ESCALATE\n- HIGH + docs ok = STANDARD_ESCALATION\n- Escalated = MANAGER_REVIEW\n- Approved = AUTO_APPROVE\n- Otherwise = STANDARD_PROCESSING",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "OdRTdgTj3Wx2aSVJDZtmo",
      "originalText": "Business Logic: Complex decision tree based on all conditions\nRules:\n- Deadline passed + escalated = ESCALATE_AND_NOTIFY\n- CRITICAL + not approved = IMMEDIATE_ESCALATION\n- HIGH + missing docs = REQUEST_DOCUMENTS_AND_ESCALATE\n- HIGH + docs ok = STANDARD_ESCALATION\n- Escalated = MANAGER_REVIEW\n- Approved = AUTO_APPROVE\n- Otherwise = STANDARD_PROCESSING",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
