      "updated": 1775513583225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Business Logic: Execute the determined final action\n    Actions:\n    - ESCALATE_AND_NOTIFY: Escalate to senior manager + send urgent notification\n    - IMMEDIATE_ESCALATION: Immediate escalation to director level\n    - EXPEDITE_PROCESSING: Fast-track processing\n    - REQUEST_DOCUMENTS_AND_ESCALATE: Request missing docs + escalate\n    - STANDARD_ESCALATION: Standard escalation process\n    - MANAGER_REVIEW: Assign to manager for review\n    - AUTO_APPROVE: Automatic approval with notification\n    - URGENT_REVIEW: Priority review due to deadline\n    - STANDARD_PROCESSING: Normal workflow processing",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "FBxVjnWTuJN7tOnVr5Yhj",
      "originalText": "Business Logic: Execute the determined final action\n    Actions:\n    - ESCALATE_AND_NOTIFY: Escalate to senior manager + send urgent notification\n    - IMMEDIATE_ESCALATION: Immediate escalation to director level\n    - EXPEDITE_PROCESSING: Fast-track processing\n    - REQUEST_DOCUMENTS_AND_ESCALATE: Request missing docs + escalate\n    - STANDARD_ESCALATION: Standard escalation process\n    - MANAGER_REVIEW: Assign to manager for review\n    - AUTO_APPROVE: Automatic approval with notification\n    - URGENT_REVIEW: Priority review due to deadline\n    - STANDARD_PROCESSING: Normal workflow processing",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
